The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques for generating theorems and proofs, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the authors use image recognition tasks as a benchmark for their approach, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the practical applications of their approach in software engineering, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
